etcd arugments
--cert-file = <path> => certs used for SSL/TLS connections to etc
--key-file = <path> => key for certificate
--advertise-client-urls  => Address etcd server bnds accepting incoming requests.
--listen-client-urls => etcd clients or other members used to contact etcd server
